{"tid":15052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"lihkg 最需要active user，創意台，同推出公海","createTime":"2016-11-30T19:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T23:03:19.000Z","uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1578b7ee063d76f6fff9c191d83612224d74cd3","tid":15052,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"冇電又要打過😥😥<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 振興新科林創意台一定要 多人 多post 活躍 </span></span>振興新科林創意台一定要 多人 多post 活躍<br />\n過往多數引致關注度爆發性增長既網絡事件都係出自創意台，改歌改圖都係台柱之一<br />\n<br />\n另外，好多巴打都忽略以前 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高登&gt;公海&gt;高登 既模式</span></span>，<br />\n所以請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用FB，share</span> 多D 高質post出公海，<br />\n<br />\n唔好妄想瓊姐呢D靠高登上位既娛樂中介(娛樂中介非KOL，KOL可以係高質user，但娛樂中介不在此列)會無條件幫手推post出公海，佢哋都係睇人數食飯，新科林冇話題嘅話就會返舊地盤收料，講高登仔點點點，唔好忽略品牌效應嘅力量，高登as a label，係可以等同香港網絡界，而lihkg未有咁既label<br />\n<br />\n更不能低估現實傾計既力量，好多人會以為FB share就有用，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網上過多既資訊會互相掩蓋，五分鐘可以睇一個post，三十個post係睇唔到半個鐘，平均一分鐘都冇，資訊愈多愈雜愈會阻礙傳播，所以現實同朋友吹水講多D有趣post，一定要提埋科林個名，就好似中學睇完高登再講比同學知咁(所以連巴快D改個順口中文名，冇民意事小，把握熱情事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n能唔能夠成就lihkg就睇各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdc330c7c5426268687e807fede3601b7ff718d","tid":15052,"uid":23282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44354a512d27c7875a210c5bf34f0f0f5b817758","tid":15052,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"Your are right"},{"pid":"5cc677a229d53b48e5e46de902b604b1baa2c62a","tid":15052,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T23:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Your are right</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠唔洗講咁多"}]}